spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:description: CORE10100 is an Ethernet Media Access Controller that connects Local Area Networks at data rates of 10 or 100 Mb/s. It supports either a Media Independent Interface (MII) or Reduced Media Independent Interface (RMII) for physical connection and implements Carrier Sense Multiple Access with Collision Detection (CSMA/CD) algorithms per IEEE 802.3
